   g2RA                tcs:sad:g2RA               0 RA or Azimuth
   g2Dec               tcs:sad:g2Dec              0 Dec or Elevation
   g2InputFrame        tcs:sad:g2InputFrame       0 Coordinate system
   g2Equinox           tcs:sad:g2Equinox          0 Equinox
   g2TrackFrame        tcs:sad:g2TrackFrame       0 Tracking frame
   g2Wavelength        tcs:sad:g2Wavelength       0 Wavelength
   g2TrackEq           tcs:sad:g2TrackEq          0 Tracking equinox
